                <![CDATA[Tesla Model 3 RW]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1224198</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>2024-2025 年度《财政预算案》宣布延长电动车首次登记税宽减安排期。在新「一换一」计划下，若购入之电动车价值不超过 HK$270,348，则无需要为电动车的首次登记缴付税款。今日 Tesla 就宣布推出 Tesla Model 3 Rear-Wheel Drive 后轮驱动版电动车，以新「一换一」计划计算后售价为 270,200 港币，可以完全享有「一换一」的全额首次登记税宽减。今日 Tesla 就邀请了小编去看看 Tesla Model 3 Rear-Wheel Drive，现在就让小编和大家分享这款 Tesla 的新电动车。</p><p><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1224203" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/img_0426-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/img_0426-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/img_0426.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1224204" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/img_0429-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/img_0429-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/img_0429.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1224205" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/img_0430-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/img_0430-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/img_0430.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1224206" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/img_0432-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/img_0432-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/img_0432.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1224222" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/img_0492-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/img_0492-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/img_0492.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>全新 8 吋后排座椅显示萤幕让后座乘客可以享受温度控制、音乐播放等功能。其中内置 Netflix、YouTube 等，更可以玩游戏。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1224211" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/img_0442-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/img_0442-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/img_0442.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲后排也可控制温度</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1224215" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/img_0456-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/img_0456-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/img_0456.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲内置 Netflix、YouTube 等</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1224213" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/img_0448-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/img_0448-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/img_0448.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲可观看 YouTube</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1224212" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-conten